<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>A new account has been created in the AFSCME Toolkit that is pending approval for <%= @user.first_name + ' ' + @user.last_name %><%= @user.affiliate ? ' from ' + @user.affiliate.title : '' %>.</p>
    <p>
      This user will not be able to use the Toolkit until an Administrator or Vetter approves their new account.
    </p>
    <p>To approve or reject accounts:<p>
      <ul>
        <li>Log into the <%= link_to "Toolkit application", new_user_session_url %> with your admin account.</li>
        <li>Visit the <%= link_to "users account page", admin_users_url %> and either approve or reject the user(s).</li>
      </ul>
  </body>
</html>